xplanation for this is consistent with the importance\nof exchange-correlation nonlocality in regions of core-valence overlap.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Mar 2009 08:50:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
